    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a mechanically sound 2008 Porsche Cayman S, featuring the venerable 3.4L flat-six powerplant mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. This mid-engine platform delivers exceptional rotational inertia and handling characteristics. Recent service includes a full cooling system refresh and inspection of the bore walls to ensure structural integrity. The suspension retains its factory damping rates, providing a communicative chassis feel through the hydraulic steering rack. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a crisp heel-and-toe friendly pedal arrangement. An ideal specimen for the driver seeking a pure, analog experience.",
