    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks and drives great! I've taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. It's ready for its next adventure, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
